<body>
<segment id="1" parent="1001" relname="preparation">Enjoy the Ice Festival in Harbin , China</segment>
<segment id="2" parent="1001" relname="joint">The Ice and Snow Festival in Harbin , China is the 2nd largest ice and snow festival in the world .</segment>
<segment id="3" parent="1004" relname="span">People come from all over the world</segment>
<segment id="4" parent="1005" relname="joint">to participate</segment>
<segment id="5" parent="1005" relname="joint">and see the results of this snow and ice competition .</segment>
<segment id="6" parent="1004" relname="elaboration">Here &apos;s how to enjoy your trip to this northern Chinese city .</segment>
<segment id="7" parent="1007" relname="preparation">Steps</segment>
<segment id="8" parent="9" relname="preparation">Choose the right timing :</segment>
<segment id="9" parent="1008" relname="span">The ice festival usually begins in early January .</segment>
<segment id="10" parent="1010" relname="span">( This may begin earlier</segment>
<segment id="11" parent="10" relname="elaboration">depending on the weather that year ) .</segment>
<segment id="12" parent="1012" relname="span">It is best to go earlier in the season ,</segment>
<segment id="13" parent="1013" relname="span">because the larger structures will be closed off</segment>
<segment id="14" parent="13" relname="circumstance">as the warm weather compromises their structure .</segment>
<segment id="15" parent="1015" relname="preparation">Be Prepared :</segment>
<segment id="16" parent="1016" relname="span">Harbin is the coldest city in China ,</segment>
<segment id="17" parent="16" relname="elaboration">located near the border with Russia .</segment>
<segment id="18" parent="1017" relname="joint">Expect temperatures well below freezing , usually between 0 and 10 degree Fahrenheit .</segment>
<segment id="19" parent="1018" relname="joint">Wear warm clothes !</segment>
<segment id="20" parent="1021" relname="span">Wear many layers and cold weather gear</segment>
<segment id="21" parent="20" relname="elaboration">( such as hats , scarves , gloves , etc. )</segment>
<segment id="22" parent="1020" relname="same_unit">You will also need warm , waterproof , winter boots for the snow .</segment>
<segment id="23" parent="1023" relname="preparation">Know where to go :</segment>
<segment id="24" parent="1023" relname="joint">The Ice and Snow Festival is not limited to one area .</segment>
<segment id="25" parent="1025" relname="span">There are several places</segment>
<segment id="26" parent="25" relname="elaboration">you can go .</segment>
<segment id="27" parent="1026" relname="joint">The largest , and by far the most popular , are the Ice and Snow World and the International Snow Sculpture Exhibition on Sun Island .</segment>
<segment id="28" parent="1027" relname="joint">The Zhaolin Gardens are also popular .</segment>
<segment id="29" parent="1029" relname="preparation">Buy tickets :</segment>
<segment id="30" parent="1030" relname="span">The entrance tickets for the different Ice and Snow Festival areas are extremely expensive .</segment>
<segment id="31" parent="30" relname="elaboration">They usually cost upwards of 300 RMB .</segment>
<segment id="32" parent="1034" relname="condition">If you have a student ID for an undergraduate degree at a Chinese university</segment>
<segment id="33" parent="1035" relname="span">( study period</segment>
<segment id="34" parent="33" relname="elaboration">lasting approx. a year )</segment>
<segment id="35" parent="1034" relname="same_unit">you can get half-price .</segment>
<segment id="36" parent="1036" relname="joint">Children &apos;s tickets are usually based on height not age .</segment>
<segment id="37" parent="1037" relname="joint">Your child &apos;s age may not guarantee a free ticket .</segment>
<segment id="38" parent="1038" relname="contrast">Elderly and Military ID &apos;s can also result in a discount ,</segment>
<segment id="39" parent="1038" relname="contrast">but this may be only for Chinese people .</segment>
<segment id="40" parent="1040" relname="span">Cheaper tickets can be purchased online or through the Harbin Tourist Center on Zhongyang St.</segment>
<segment id="41" parent="40" relname="elaboration">( 中央大街 ) .</segment>
<segment id="42" parent="1042" relname="preparation">Know when to go :</segment>
<segment id="43" parent="1042" relname="joint">Sun Island &apos;s Snow Sculpture Exhibition closes before sunset .</segment>
<segment id="44" parent="1043" relname="span">The Ice and Snow World is open almost all day .</segment>
<segment id="45" parent="1045" relname="joint">It is best to go just before sundown</segment>
<segment id="46" parent="1046" relname="span">and stay</segment>
<segment id="47" parent="46" relname="circumstance">while it &apos;s dark .</segment>
<segment id="48" parent="1048" relname="preparation">This is where the famous 冰灯 are located .</segment>
<segment id="49" parent="1048" relname="joint">Zhaolin Gardens is best viewed after sundown as well .</segment>
<segment id="50" parent="1050" relname="preparation">Find convenient transportation :</segment>
<segment id="51" parent="1051" relname="span">Ice and Snow World and the Snow Sculpture Exhibition are both located on Sun Island ,</segment>
<segment id="52" parent="1052" relname="span">which is farther from the city center</segment>
<segment id="53" parent="52" relname="elaboration">( and most likely even farther from your hotel ) .</segment>
<segment id="54" parent="1056" relname="span">There are bus lines</segment>
<segment id="55" parent="54" relname="elaboration">that go to the exhibitions and Snow World on Sun Island .</segment>
<segment id="56" parent="1057" relname="joint">These cost a measly 2 RMB</segment>
<segment id="57" parent="1057" relname="joint">and are direct lines .</segment>
<segment id="58" parent="59" relname="preparation">Some hotels offer free shuttles .</segment>
<segment id="59" parent="1058" relname="span">You can hire a bus or a taxi .</segment>
<segment id="60" parent="1060" relname="preparation">Note that taxis do not use meters in Harbin .</segment>
<segment id="61" parent="1061" relname="span">You will have to agree on a price</segment>
<segment id="62" parent="61" relname="circumstance">before you arrive .</segment>
<segment id="63" parent="1063" relname="span">For the adventurous , the river separating Sun Island and the main area of Harbin has a gondola</segment>
<segment id="64" parent="63" relname="elaboration">which will take you to the other side .</segment>
<segment id="65" parent="1064" relname="joint">From there , it &apos;s just a short walk .</segment>
<segment id="66" parent="1066" relname="span">Follow these steps</segment>
<segment id="67" parent="66" relname="circumstance">when you get there :</segment>
<segment id="68" parent="1068" relname="preparation">Bring a camera !</segment>
<segment id="69" parent="1069" relname="span">There are many beautiful hand-carved ice and snow sculptures</segment>
<segment id="70" parent="69" relname="elaboration">you wo n&apos;t want to forget .</segment>
<segment id="71" parent="1071" relname="preparation">Try sledding !</segment>
<segment id="72" parent="1072" relname="span">Several places , particularly the Ice and Snow World , have several ice slides .</segment>
<segment id="73" parent="1073" relname="joint">You do n&apos;t even need a sled !</segment>
<segment id="74" parent="1074" relname="joint">The biggest ice slide is in Ice and Snow World .</segment>
<segment id="75" parent="1076" relname="joint">They provide sleds</segment>
<segment id="76" parent="1076" relname="joint">and it &apos;s free .</segment>
<segment id="77" parent="1077" relname="contrast">Take pictures with winter animals like snow foxes ,</segment>
<segment id="78" parent="1078" relname="span">or ride in a carriage</segment>
<segment id="79" parent="78" relname="elaboration">pulled by horses , reindeer , or dogs .</segment>
<segment id="80" parent="1080" relname="preparation">Tips</segment>
<segment id="81" parent="1082" relname="span">There are very few places</segment>
<segment id="82" parent="81" relname="purpose">to eat in these places</segment>
<segment id="83" parent="1083" relname="span">so it may be a good idea</segment>
<segment id="84" parent="83" relname="purpose">to eat beforehand .</segment>
<segment id="85" parent="1081" relname="elaboration">Otherwise , there are candied fruits and other snacks available .</segment>
